  <exercise>
   <p>
    A ball, a cylinder, and a ring each of mass 10 kg and radius 0.1 m are released 
    from rest at the top of an inclined plane 2 m long. 
    Which will reach the bottom of the plane the fastest? Why?
   </p>
  </exercise>
 
  <exercise>
