      A wagon wheel consists of a rim of mass 50 kg and diameter 60 cm 
      and eight spokes each with a mass of 2 kg. What is the moment of inertia of the wheel?
    </p>
  </exercise>

  <exercise>
    <p>
      A rectangular block has a length of 20 cm, 
      a width of 10 cm, a height of 5 cm, and a mass of 4 kg. 
      What is its moment of inertia about its three principle axes?
    </p>
  </exercise>

